&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;ezCater is the #1 food tech platform for workplaces in the US. The company makes it easy for any organization to manage its food needs and order from over 125,000 restaurants nationwide. For workplaces, ezCater provides flexible and scalable solutions for everything from employee meal programs to one-off meetings, all backed by beyond helpful 24/7 service and business-grade reliability. For restaurant partners, ezCater helps grow their business by bringing them new high-value customers and large orders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Customer Engagement Manager to join our Growth team and own retention for our high value Meal Program accounts. This is an individual contributor role focused on proactively building deep customer relationships, driving account retention, and serving as the primary strategic partner for ezCater&#39;s top Meal Program customers.&lt;/p&gt;
