&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;ezCater is the #1 food tech platform for workplaces in the US. The company makes it easy for any organization to manage its food needs and order from over 125,000 restaurants nationwide. For workplaces, ezCater provides flexible and scalable solutions for everything from employee meal programs to one-off meetings, all backed by beyond helpful 24/7 service and business-grade reliability. For restaurant partners, ezCater helps grow their business by bringing them new high-value customers and large orders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;The Product Management team is looking for an experienced Principal Product Manager to focus on ezCater’s Fintech portfolio.&amp;nbsp; In this position, you will partner with our Finance team to develop enterprise class solutions in the areas of B2B and B2C payments, partner payouts, fraud management, tax solutions, and regulatory technology. You will define our financial platform strategy and align products and processes across product, engineering, finance and external teams.&lt;/p&gt;
