&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;ezCater is the #1 food tech platform for workplaces in the US. The company makes it easy for any organization to manage its food needs and order from over 125,000 restaurants nationwide. For workplaces, ezCater provides flexible and scalable solutions for everything from employee meal programs to one-off meetings, all backed by beyond helpful 24/7 service and business-grade reliability. For restaurant partners, ezCater helps grow their business by bringing them new high-value customers and large orders.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;As Senior Product Designer for Admin Experiences, you’ll sit at the center of how companies of all sizes manage food at work – and how ezCater earns the trust of the business buyers and admins who make that possible. You’ll work across two tightly connected areas:&lt;/p&gt;
