&lt;li style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead discovery grounded in how businesses actually buy and manage food &lt;/strong&gt;by partnering with Sales, Account Management, Support, and Research to understand the realities of enterprise procurement, program administration, and organizational complexity.&lt;/li&gt;
