&lt;li&gt;Drive the vision and develop a roadmap for a delivery platform for our restaurant and delivery partners.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop internal tools to ensure our team can effectively monitor and manage delivery partners&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tell a compelling story using research and data to evangelize the roadmap and vision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build deep empathy for ezCater users and become their biggest champion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead product initiatives and work collaboratively across a cross-functional team including Design, Research, Engineering, Data Analysis, ML/AI and other Product Managers to define, prioritize, and build new functionalities and improved user experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Continuously identify areas for innovation and improvement, and implement strategies to keep us ahead, ensuring our marketplace delivers an unparalleled user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create and monitor the ongoing metrics that measure and define success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Travel to Boston quarterly for planning and business reviews&lt;/li&gt;
